"DOTA_Item_Strange_Modifier_Sven_DoubleStuns"	"Sær Modifikator: Multi-helts-Storm Hammers"
"[english]DOTA_Item_Strange_Modifier_Sven_DoubleStuns"	"Strange Modifier: Multi-Hero Storm Hammers"
"DOTA_Item_Desc_Strange_Modifier_Sven_DoubleStuns"	"Ved at sætte denne Sære Modifikator på en valgfri Sær genstand, gør du den i stand til at spore antallet af Storm Hammers, som har ramt mindst to fjendtlige helte, mens du er udstyret med den som Sven."
"[english]DOTA_Item_Desc_Strange_Modifier_Sven_DoubleStuns"	"Adding this Strange Modifier to a strange item of your choice will allow it to also count the number of your Storm Hammers that hit at least two enemy Heroes while wearing it as Sven."

"[english]DOTA_Item_Desc_Strange_Modifier_Sven_WarcryAssists"	"Adding this Strange Modifier to a strange item of your choice will allow it to also count the number of enemy Heroes your Warcry-buffed allies kill while wearing it as Sven."

"DOTA_Item_Pennant_DK"	"DK-fane"
"[english]DOTA_Item_Pennant_DK"	"DK Pennant"
"DOTA_Item_Desc_Pennant_DK"	"Vis din støtte til DK ved at købe denne holdfane. Udstyr den i \"fanepositionen\" i dit spillerudstyr for at vise andre tilskuere, hvem du hepper på. Opgrader den for at vise, at du mener det! Desuden vil udstyrelse af en fane gøre dig berettiget til genstandsdrops, mens du ser på dit holds kampe direkte under The International 2012 og andre turneringer, som Valve vil understøtte i fremtiden. DK-faner kan kombineres med andre DK-faner for at opgradere din holdfanes faneniveau. Niveauet på din holdfane vil øge fanværdien i alt for holdet, som du ser på i en turneringskamp."
"[english]DOTA_Item_Desc_Pennant_DK"	"Show your support for DK by buying this Team Pennant! Equip it in the 'fan slot' of your Player Loadout to show other spectators who you're rooting for. Upgrade it to show you mean business! In addition, equipping a pennant makes you eligible for item drops while you spectate your team's matches live during the International 2012, and other tournaments Valve may designate in the future.  DK pennants can be combined with other DK pennants to upgrade your Team Pennant fan level.  The level of your Team Pennant will increase the total fan value of the team when you are spectating a Tournament match."

Double click or right-click the key in your backpack and select the chest you want to open.
After the end of September 3rd, 2012 this will become a normal key."

"DOTA_Item_Desc_Pennant_Mousesports"	"Vis din støtte til Mousesports ved at købe denne holdfane. Udstyr den i \"fanepositionen\" i dit spillerudstyr for at vise andre tilskuere, hvem du hepper på. Opgrader den for at vise, at du mener det! Desuden vil udstyrelse af en fane gøre dig berettiget til genstandsdrops, mens du ser på dit holds kampe direkte under The International 2012 og andre turneringer, som Valve vil understøtte i fremtiden. Mousesports-faner kan kombineres med andre Mousesports-faner for at opgradere din holdfanes faneniveau. Niveauet på din holdfane vil øge fanværdien i alt for holdet, som du ser på i en turneringskamp."
"[english]DOTA_Item_Desc_Pennant_Mousesports"	"Show your support for Mousesports by buying this Team Pennant! Equip it in the 'fan slot' of your Player Loadout to show other spectators who you're rooting for. Upgrade it to show you mean business! In addition, equipping a pennant makes you eligible for item drops while you spectate your team's matches live during the International 2012, and other tournaments Valve may designate in the future.  Mousesports pennants can be combined with other Mousesports pennants to upgrade your Team Pennant fan level.  The level of your Team Pennant will increase the total fan value of the team when you are spectating a Tournament match."
